tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE qubits (id INT PRIMARY KEY, state TEXT);
CREATE TABLE entanglement (id INT PRIMARY KEY, qubit_1 INT, qubit_2 INT, FOREIGN KEY (qubit_1) REFERENCES qubits(id), FOREIGN KEY (qubit_2) REFERENCES qubits(id));
CREATE TABLE quantum_computers (id INT PRIMARY KEY, model TEXT, qubit_count INT, manufacturer TEXT);
CREATE TABLE qubits (id UUID PRIMARY KEY, state VARCHAR);
CREATE TABLE quantum_gates (gate_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, gate_name VARCHAR);
CREATE TABLE quantum_circuits (circuit_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, circuit_name VARCHAR, num_qubits INT);
CREATE TABLE quantum_algorithms (algorithm_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, algorithm_name VARCHAR, description TEXT);
CREATE TABLE qubits (id INT PRIMARY KEY, value FLOAT);
CREATE TABLE quantum_gates (id INT PRIMARY KEY, gate_name TEXT, gate_matrix TEXT);
CREATE TABLE quantum_circuits (id INT PRIMARY KEY, circuit_name TEXT, circuit_description TEXT);
CREATE TABLE quantum_algorithms (id INT PRIMARY KEY, algorithm_name TEXT, algorithm_description TEXT);
CREATE TABLE quantum_measurements (id INT PRIMARY KEY, measurement_name TEXT, measurement_result FLOAT);
